reviewText: My daughter loves B. Bears. All of their DVD's are made well.

In case you thought you were getting all new episodes, be aware that the 5 episodes on this dvd are all found on other berenstain bear dvds, just they repackaged this with a different name.  The episodes on this one are:
Go to School
Trouble at School
Homework Hassle
Jump Rope Contest
The In Crowd
